Apply C.A.S.A security policies when touching auth, permissions, secrets, public APIs, logs, uploads or infrastructure.

Required:

- validate external input
- keep authorization server-side
- avoid logging secrets or sensitive data
- update threat model or security notes when risk changes
- run relevant sensors
